NAME
	query_mortal - test if a player is a mortal

SYNOPSIS
	int query_mortal(object arg)

DESCRIPTION
	Check if 'arg' is a mortal player object.

RETURN VALUE
	Returns 1 if 'arg' is a mortal player object, 0 otherwise.

EXAMPLES
	if (query_mortal(this_player()) {
	   write("You can't seem to quite figure it out.\n");
	}

SEE ALSO
	safun/query_admin, safun/query_guest, safun/query_user_type,
	safun/query_wizard
